desc_short	-----								Tower defense as you've never experienced it before. We take tower defense to your home, your neighbor's house, the Seattle Space Needle, or anywhere in the world; the choice is yours. World Defense is the first, physics based, 3d tower defense where anything and everything depends upon real world simulations.							
